items.title: Diddy trial live updates: Cassie cross-examination continues
items.description: Cassie Ventura is back on the stand in Sean "Diddy" Combs' trial for what prosecutors hope will be her final day.

items.title: 2 climbers die on Mount Everest, unclear if bodies will be retrieved
items.description: Two people died while climbing Mount Everest as hundreds of climbers are attempting to scale the world's highest peak, expedition organizers said.

items.title: Most Americans don't earn enough to afford costs of living, study finds
